videos.description: PJ Washington starts the game off hot, hitting a jumper over his Tennessee defender.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Washington hits nice hook shot for Kentucky) 2019/2/16

videos.headline: Washington hits nice hook shot for Kentucky

videos.description: Keldon Johnson pulls up from behind the arc, scoring 11 consecutive points including three 3-pointers against Tennessee.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnson catches fire early, drains 3 triples) 2019/2/16

videos.headline: Johnson catches fire early, drains 3 triples

videos.description: Grant Williams shows off on defense, coming up with a nice steal to set up Lamonte Turner with a basket on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams steals it for Vols bucket) 2019/2/16

videos.headline: Williams steals it for Vols bucket

videos.description: Ashton Hagans puts a nice move on his defender in the paint before dishing the ball Keldon Johnson who finishes at the rim for two.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnson's crafty bucket puts Kentucky up 20 over Tennessee) 2019/2/16

videos.headline: Johnson's crafty bucket puts Kentucky up 20 over Tennessee

videos.description: Reid Travis rises up for a massive rejection on Tennessee and in transition Kentucky converts with a powerful EJ Montgomery putback.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Travis' block leads to powerful Montgomery slam) 2019/2/16

videos.headline: Travis' block leads to powerful Montgomery slam

videos.description: Tyler Herro doesn't give up as he picks up his own miss twice and then finally gets it to fall while being fouled.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Herro sticks with it and dumps in jumper on third try) 2019/2/16

videos.headline: Herro sticks with it and dumps in jumper on third try

videos.description: Kentucky coach John Calipari waves off the crowd and tells them to stop chanting "overrated" at Tennessee.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Calipari tries to stop Vols 'overrated' chants from crowd) 2019/2/16

videos.headline: Calipari tries to stop Vols 'overrated' chants from crowd

videos.description: PJ Washington, Tyler Herro and Keldon Johnson tell Maria Taylor about the statement the Wildcats made against Tennessee in an 86-69 victory.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Wildcats 'feel like' a Final Four team) 2019/2/16

videos.headline: Wildcats 'feel like' a Final Four team
